    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Good to know @apolcyn, thanks for looking into it!\r\n\r\n> How severe is this bug for you?\r\n\r\nWe can work around it with circuit breakers. We'd use those anyway in hot paths, so it's not a huge deal for us, but it could cause problems for anyone not using circuit breakers and expecting that fail-fast applies to DNS resolution failures."
